OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FAn ITV News investigation finds that
OL,8,Ftens of thousands of children across
OL,9,Fthe UK targeted on Snapchat, with
OL,10,Foffences including rape and sexual
OL,11,Fassault, as UK Editor Paul Brand
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FA warning this report contains
OL,15,Fdistressing details.
OL,17,FThe social media app Snapchat is being
OL,18,Fused by paedophiles and violent
OL,19,Fcriminals to target thousands of
OL,20,Fchildren a year, an ITV News
OL,21,Finvestigation has found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
