PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781179881
OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FAcross 37 police forces, there were
OL,8,Fmore than 100,000 offences involving
OL,9,Fthe app over the past five years.
OL,11,FIt's not always clear how Snapchat was
OL,12,Finvolved, but the crimes include
OL,13,Fmultiple cases of rape and sexual
OL,14,Fassault.
OL,16,FWhere police forces gave the age of
OL,17,Fthe victims, six out of ten were
OL,18,Fchildren. The youngest was just seven
OL,19,Fyears old.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
