OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FOur findings come as the government
OL,8,Fconsiders banning social media apps
OL,9,Ffor under-16s.
OL,11,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,12,FSecretary, Liz Kendall, told ITV News
OL,13,Fthat she felt "horror" and "fear" at
OL,14,Fthe findings.
OL,16,FGiving the strongest hint yet that she
OL,17,Fwould like to ban social media for
OL,18,Funder 16s, she said, "I think the
OL,19,Freason why parents have been so
OL,20,Fsupportive of a ban is because of the
OL,21,Fsimplicity".
