OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FOur investigation reveals how the
OL,8,Fonline often transfers to the offline,
OL,9,Fwith paedophiles repeatedly using
OL,10,FSnapchat to locate children in real
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FAmong recent victims was 11-year-old
OL,14,F'Sophie', whose name we have changed
OL,15,Fto protect her lifetime anonymity.
OL,17,FIn 2022, she was sent explicit
OL,18,Fphotographs by a user who called
OL,19,Fhimself Tom Bailey and claimed to be
OL,20,F19.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/26
