OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FIt's thought he had managed to find
OL,8,Fher via Snapmap, which allows users to
OL,9,Fsearch for other people ` including
OL,10,Fchildren - in their area.
OL,12,F"Hope u like xxx," he messaged out of
OL,13,Fthe blue one morning before school as
OL,14,FSophie was getting ready, after
OL,15,Fsending her a photo of a man in his
OL,16,Funderwear.
OL,18,F"Like to see more xxx," he added. "I'm
OL,19,Fin derby and 19 u?"
