OL,7,F"I'm 11, go away," Sophie's family
OL,8,Freplied on her behalf, after she
OL,9,Falerted them to what was happening.
OL,11,F"Oh nice," her predator persisted, "My
OL,12,Fex was 13 lol".
OL,14,F"Bet your well fit," he told her. "You
OL,15,Fdone anything wiv a boy".
OL,17,F"I'm 11 years old," Sophie's family
OL,18,Freplied again, hoping to warn him off.
