OL,7,F"The messages carried on coming
OL,8,Fthrough quite quickly, and they were
OL,9,Fgetting quite vile. It was crude and
OL,10,Fdisgusting. I was physically sick,"
OL,11,FSophie's mum told me.
OL,13,FPolice managed to track down her
OL,14,Fpredator, whose real name is Mark
OL,15,FRayworth - a 55-year-old paedophile
OL,16,Fwho was working as a bathroom fitter.
OL,18,FHe was arrested and convicted of
OL,19,Fattempting to engage in sexual
OL,20,Factivity with Sophie.
