OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FBut because of Snapchat's location
OL,8,Ffeature, she became terrified that he
OL,9,Fwould be able to track her down.
OL,11,F"It was quite scary," she told me. "It
OL,12,Fmade me really paranoid even to go out
OL,13,Fwith family. I was worried that he
OL,14,Fwould be upset that I'd told people,
OL,15,Fthat he'd hurt my family for reporting
OL,16,Fit."
OL,18,FSophie's parents had to install CCTV
OL,19,Fat their house to reassure her.
