OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,F"I don't see that there's any need for
OL,8,Fmaps to be on any apps that children
OL,9,Faccess," her mum told me. "Anyone can
OL,10,Flocate them. I don't see how that
OL,11,Fserves any purpose to any child."
OL,13,FIt is possible to turn the location
OL,14,Fsettings off on Snapchat, but parents
OL,15,Fhave told us that they didn't even
OL,16,Frealise the function existed in the
OL,17,Ffirst place.
