OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FAlready in 2026, dozens of paedophiles
OL,8,Fhave been sentenced for targeting
OL,9,Fchildren via the app, some using it to
OL,10,Flocate their victims in real life.
OL,12,FIn April, 27-year-old Kieron Oldham
OL,13,Ffrom Barnsley pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Fsexually assaulting a 13-year-old girl
OL,15,Fafter tracking her location on
OL,16,FSnapchat to a local park.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/26
