OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FIn February, 31-year-old Ross Brogan
OL,8,Ffrom Glasgow was jailed after adding
OL,9,Fchildren at random on Snapchat before
OL,10,Foffering payment for explicit photos
OL,11,Fand then blackmailing them to elicit
OL,12,Fmore.
OL,14,FHe went on to sexually abuse one 13-
OL,15,Fyear-old boy in person.
OL,17,FAnd in May, 35-year-old Siah Riley
OL,18,Ffrom Derby was jailed after grooming
OL,19,Fmore than 150 children online,
OL,20,Fincluding on Snapchat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/26
