OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FWith more than 20 million users in the
OL,8,FUK, Snapchat is one of the most widely
OL,9,Fused social media platforms.
OL,11,FThe National Crime Agency (NCA) told
OL,12,FITV News it is this popularity -
OL,13,Fparticularly with children - that
OL,14,Fattracts its offenders.
OL,16,FIn 2025, the NCA saw 92,000 self-
OL,17,Freferred cases of potential child
OL,18,Fabuse from tech companies - and that
OL,19,Ffigure has increased this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/26
