PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781179881
OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FLast month alone, there were 400
OL,8,Freferrals each day - and 100 of those
OL,9,Fcame from Snapchat.
OL,11,F"Snapchat is obviously one of the most
OL,12,Fpopular platforms for children... But
OL,13,Fas a result it is absolutely used by
OL,14,Foffenders and all the time," says NCA
OL,15,FDirector General Graeme Biggar.
OL,17,F"This is a company that we work with.
OL,18,FThey have made changes to their
OL,19,Fplatform. But even with those changes
OL,20,Fthere's 100 referrals a day - more has
OL,21,Fto happen."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/26
