OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FITV News has learnt that paedophiles
OL,8,Fare even using Snapmap to target
OL,9,Fchildren while they are at school,
OL,10,Fwith the location function helping
OL,11,Fthem to identify particular hotspots
OL,12,Fwhere minors are interacting on the
OL,13,Fapp.
OL,15,FLast month, a school in northern
OL,16,FEngland wrote to parents, warning them
OL,17,Fthat a user was targeting multiple
OL,18,Fpupils.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/26
