OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FAmong them was 12-year-old Zara (not
OL,8,Fher real name), whose mother received
OL,9,Fan email from staff, alerting her that
OL,10,Fthe school "has become aware of a man
OL,11,Fin his 20s called Max making and
OL,12,Ftrying to make contact with younger
OL,13,Fgirls", including Zara.
OL,15,F"It took me about four days to get
OL,16,Faccess to her phone," her mother told
OL,17,Fme.
OL,19,F"She just shut off completely, like
OL,20,Fshe was in trouble. Then she kind of
OL,21,Fopened up."
