PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781179881
OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FZara told her mother that the unknown
OL,8,Fuser had asked her for pictures. At
OL,9,Ffirst, they were requests for photos
OL,10,Fof what she was eating or where she
OL,11,Fwas, as well as pictures of her family.
OL,13,FBut eventually, she was asked for
OL,14,Fsexual photos of herself.
OL,16,FZara's mother was devastated to learn
OL,17,Fthat her daughter had sent one.
OL,19,F"I was overwhelmed with fear, sick and
OL,20,Fguilt," her mum said. "I had no idea
OL,21,Fwhat was going on".
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@GO]|D@WOU}D@RO]
