OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781179881
OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FBoth Zara and her mum are terrified
OL,8,Fthat the photograph might still be in
OL,9,Fcirculation.
OL,11,F"I've always tried to protect my kids
OL,12,Ffrom the monsters on the outside,"
OL,13,FZara's mum told me. "But actually the
OL,14,Fwhole time the monster was actually in
OL,15,Fmy home, in my children's bedroom, on
OL,16,Ftheir phones".
OL,18,F"If I had my way, the app would be
OL,19,Fgone. Deleted, gone, banned," she said.
