OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FIn May, Ofcom ` which regulates online
OL,8,Fplatforms ` also announced that
OL,9,FSnapchat had promised to make changes
OL,10,Fto its app to stop adults from
OL,11,Fcontacting children.
OL,13,FBut parents have told us that they do
OL,14,Fnot trust tech companies to implement
OL,15,Fthe changes and want social media apps
OL,16,F` particularly Snapchat ` banned for
OL,17,Fchildren.
OL,19,FIt sounds as if the secretary of state
OL,20,Fagrees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/26
