CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781179881
OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,F"We'll be coming forward with our
OL,8,Fproposals imminently," Liz Kendall
OL,9,Ftold me.
OL,11,F"But I think about parents who are
OL,12,Fcrying out for help. They want to do
OL,13,Fthe right thing, they want to make
OL,14,Fsure their children are safe, but it's
OL,15,Freally difficult to keep on top of all
OL,16,Fof these apps. So I think the reason
OL,17,Fwhy parents have been so supportive of
OL,18,Fa ban is because of the simplicity.
OL,19,FIt's a clear message about
OL,20,Fexpectations."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@VO]sD@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30822
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781179881
OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FOthers, including the National Crime
OL,8,FAgency and the children's charity the
OL,9,FNSPCC, worry that children will
OL,10,Fcircumvent a ban and believe it would
OL,11,Fbe better to improve safety on apps by
OL,12,Fremoving certain features.
OL,14,FRather than a strict social media ban,
OL,15,Fthe NCA have instead proposed tech
OL,16,Fgiants redesign the features that put
OL,17,Fits users at risk - such as the mass
OL,18,Fdiscoverability of children and weak
OL,19,Fage verification processes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30823
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1781179881
OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,F"It's the features that are most
OL,8,Fimportant to address. Remove those
OL,9,Fdangerous features or make them safe
OL,10,Fand then you could have an online
OL,11,Fenvironment that's safe for children.
OL,12,FThat's what we see from our law
OL,13,Fenforcement perspective."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/26
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
