OL,3,CA 'safe haven' for paedophiles `
OL,4,Cthousands of children abused on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,F"We are arresting over a thousand
OL,8,Fpeople each and every month who are
OL,9,Fcommitting this kind of abuse (on
OL,10,Fsocial media apps) and safeguarding
OL,11,F1,200 children each and every month,
OL,12,Fbut it's a huge challenge and we need
OL,13,Fto turn off the tap that is allowing
OL,14,Fit to happen."
OL,16,FBut Liz Kendall does not seem to think
OL,17,Fthat change can be left up to the tech
OL,18,Fcompanies.
