OL,7,F"They've had their chance," she said.
OL,8,F"Time and time and time again, they've
OL,9,Fhave had a chance to put this right.
OL,10,FThe question isn't if we're going to
OL,11,Fact, it's how."
OL,13,FIn response to our investigation,
OL,14,FSnapchat told us, "The stories shared
OL,15,Fby these families are devastating.
OL,16,FSexual exploitation is an abhorrent
OL,17,Fcrime, and we are working hard to
OL,18,Fcombat it, including by continuously
OL,19,Fevolving our safety mechanisms as
OL,20,Fcriminals change their tactics.
